OL,3,CFuneral director admits preventing
OL,4,Cburial charges
OL,6,FA funeral director has pleaded guilty
OL,7,Fat Hull Crown Court to 30 counts of
OL,8,Fpreventing a lawful and decent burial
OL,9,Fover bodies found at his business in
OL,10,F2024.
OL,12,FRobert Bush was arrested after an
OL,13,Finvestigation into the discovery of
OL,14,Fhuman remains at Legacy Independent
OL,15,FFuneral Directors in Hull in May 2024.
OL,17,FPolice launched the investigation
OL,18,Fafter concerns were raised about "care
OL,19,Ffor the deceased."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/5
