OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1775131865
OL,3,CFuneral director admits preventing
OL,4,Cburial charges
OL,6,FAppearing Hull Crown Court on Thursday
OL,7,F2 April, wearing a dark blue suit and
OL,8,Fpurple tie, he pleaded guilty to 30
OL,9,Fdifferent counts of preventing a
OL,10,Flawful and decent burial.
OL,12,FHe also pleaded guilty to theft from
OL,13,F12 charities including the Salvation
OL,14,FArmy and Macmillan Cancer Support.
OL,16,FAt October's hearing, Bush admitted 30
OL,17,Fcounts of fraud by false
OL,18,Frepresentation relating to the same 30
OL,19,Fpeople.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
