OL,3,CFuneral director admits preventing
OL,4,Cburial charges
OL,6,FA month after the investigation
OL,7,Fstarted, Humberside Police said it had
OL,8,Freceived more than 2,000 calls on a
OL,9,Fdedicated phone line from families
OL,10,Fconcerned about their loved ones'
OL,11,Fashes.
OL,13,FHe will be sentenced on 27 July, he
OL,14,Fhas been given bail until that date.
OL,16,FMore to follow.
